Settled product decision: the linked account counterpart is called
'teammate' — not 'Investment Partner', 'journey partner', or 'co-pilot'.

DB table journey_partner and all .from('journey_partner') references
are unchanged — table rename requires a separate migration.
Internal variable names (hasPartnerInvite, activePartner, etc.)
are unchanged — purely infrastructure, not user-facing.
